The paper deals with estimating the creation date of web resources, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and digital libraries (cs.DL). It also involves analyzing web archives (cs.CR) and social media data (cs.SI) to gather evidence for the creation date. Additionally, the paper mentions examining HTTP response headers (cs.CL) to estimate the creation date.
